description: Triangle, read by rows, where T(n,k) equals the dot product of the vector of terms in row n that are to the right of T(n,k) with the vector of terms in column k that are above T(n,k): T(n,k) = Sum_{j=0..n-k-1} T(n,j+k+1)*T(j+k,k) for n > k+1 > 0, with T(n,n) = 1 and T(n,n-1) = n (n>=1).
